39:58.640 --> 40:00.119
What is he doing here?

40:00.120 --> 40:01.239
He's cooperating.

40:01.240 --> 40:02.359
He's a target.

40:02.360 --> 40:03.879
Roy's the target.

40:03.880 --> 40:05.359
How is he cooperating?

40:05.360 --> 40:06.839
It's an ongoing situation.

40:06.840 --> 40:09.199
He's been a cancer
in that place for years.

40:09.200 --> 40:10.519
And now I'm here to make amends.

40:10.520 --> 40:12.480
Shut up - you're here
to save your arse.

40:14.200 --> 40:17.079
You can't let him walk for the sake
of a few more years for Roy.

40:17.080 --> 40:18.719
A few more years?

40:18.720 --> 40:20.999
I want Roy to go in there and
never come out,

40:21.000 --> 40:23.160
and you've given me
money laundering.

40:24.600 --> 40:26.960
What did you mean,
an ongoing situation?

40:28.040 --> 40:29.800
Thanks for your help.

40:32.240 --> 40:34.479
You've gone rogue.

40:34.480 --> 40:36.559
I'm calling this in.

40:36.560 --> 40:38.399
She was a grandmother, was she not?

40:38.400 --> 40:39.519
Who?

40:39.520 --> 40:42.559
The women in Craigmillar
that the kid mowed down.

40:42.560 --> 40:44.560
The kid that got the mistrial.

40:45.800 --> 40:47.399
What are you two doing?

40:47.400 --> 40:48.959
Thanks for your help.

40:48.960 --> 40:50.240
And stay out of Leith.

40:54.160 --> 40:56.879
What's happening in Leith?

40:56.880 --> 40:59.679
What did you think he'd do when
you gave him the file?

40:59.680 --> 41:01.639
You're setting up Max.

41:01.640 --> 41:03.159
For Roy.

41:03.160 --> 41:06.479
What Max has come up with,
Roy could get out of in his sleep.

41:06.480 --> 41:09.319
Maybe there's another way
that Max can serve the cause.

41:09.320 --> 41:10.479
You can't do that.

41:10.480 --> 41:12.919
I'm not sure you're a good judge
of what a copper can't do.

41:12.920 --> 41:15.199
I get information for Roy,
a wee bit of driving,

41:15.200 --> 41:16.639
but that's about it... Exactly.

41:16.640 --> 41:18.399
You can't give me Roy either.

41:18.400 --> 41:19.599
So I'll get him myself.

41:19.600 --> 41:20.720
You can't!

41:21.840 --> 41:23.960
And what can you give me instead?

41:29.320 --> 41:32.599
Last week, Roy asked me to give him
an address from a car reg.

41:32.600 --> 41:36.599
The next day, I was out in the car
and I heard it on the radio.

41:36.600 --> 41:39.480
I made sure I got there first
to see what he'd done.

41:40.880 --> 41:42.400
To see what I'd done.

41:43.960 --> 41:45.559
It was a stabbing.

41:45.560 --> 41:47.639
Close enough to the heart
for attempted murder,

41:47.640 --> 41:48.959
and it was Roy.

41:48.960 --> 41:50.639
He wouldn't do it himself.

41:50.640 --> 41:52.519
He would if she told him to.

41:52.520 --> 41:54.079
Who?

41:54.080 --> 41:55.880
The Wicked Witch of the East.

42:01.720 --> 42:03.160
We've taken the land.

42:05.320 --> 42:07.000
Taken it and sold it.

42:08.880 --> 42:10.080
You and Max?

42:12.840 --> 42:14.360
I'm going to meet him now.

42:17.840 --> 42:20.280
I can understand why
you might do that.

42:22.440 --> 42:24.399
I thought I was doing it
because of you.

42:24.400 --> 42:26.160
Now I realise it's because of her.

42:27.480 --> 42:29.720
Everything's because of her.

42:32.440 --> 42:34.560
I wish I'd known you better.

42:35.760 --> 42:37.240
Understood you better.

42:39.520 --> 42:40.960
But it's too late.

42:44.520 --> 42:47.719
I'm doing it to find something
honest, something good.

42:47.720 --> 42:49.759
And I'm...

42:49.760 --> 42:51.159
..going to go meet him now.

42:51.160 --> 42:53.079
We're going to go
somewhere that's...

42:53.080 --> 42:54.400
..not here.

43:05.160 --> 43:08.079
Beware of false prophets...

43:08.080 --> 43:11.279
..who come to you in
sheep's clothing,

43:11.280 --> 43:13.720
but inwardly are ravening wolves.

43:16.840 --> 43:18.799
I don't remember much
from that place,

43:18.800 --> 43:20.599
but I remember the hypocrisy.

43:20.600 --> 43:22.120
I remember the wolves.

43:25.640 --> 43:27.520
That may not surprise you.

43:29.040 --> 43:31.199
But this might.

43:31.200 --> 43:32.439
TV TURNS ON

43:32.440 --> 43:35.559
ON TV: There's something else.
More recent.

43:35.560 --> 43:37.719
Roy and the daughter.

43:37.720 --> 43:40.079
I'm still working it out.

43:40.080 --> 43:42.919
But I think someone
may have been killed.

43:42.920 --> 43:44.759
Maybe at our house.

43:44.760 --> 43:47.999
Over the money that he brought me.

43:48.000 --> 43:49.479
Joe MacLean.

43:49.480 --> 43:52.879
He was found off the woods last
week, wrote it down as suicide.

43:52.880 --> 43:55.039
But it wasn't.

43:55.040 --> 43:56.600
TV TURNS OFF

44:00.440 --> 44:03.159
They've got nothing on us.

44:03.160 --> 44:05.119
Except Max.

44:05.120 --> 44:06.800
Max gives them a shot.

44:13.440 --> 44:15.280
What are you going to do?

44:16.640 --> 44:18.200
Don't meet him.

44:19.480 --> 44:20.960
He won't be there.

44:25.760 --> 44:27.560
Why can't I escape?

44:28.560 --> 44:31.400
You, her, this world of
endless fucking liars.

44:35.280 --> 44:38.120
You'll never know the lives
your mother and I were given.

44:40.720 --> 44:44.479
The wreckage that we crawled from.

44:44.480 --> 44:46.759
We were sent into life unarmed,

44:46.760 --> 44:48.160
and it showed.

44:51.080 --> 44:53.840
I'm sorry for what that
meant for you.

44:55.840 --> 44:57.319
It ruined me.

44:57.320 --> 44:59.319
No.

44:59.320 --> 45:00.840
You survived.

45:02.040 --> 45:04.120
And now, you'll do more than that.

45:05.880 --> 45:08.480
You can't not, the woman you are.

45:10.440 --> 45:13.400
I just don't know how many more
chances I'll get to say that.

45:15.520 --> 45:17.840
Because life might
pull us apart again.

45:19.560 --> 45:22.280
And I wish I had the education
to say it better.

45:25.960 --> 45:28.599
The pride I feel.

45:28.600 --> 45:30.440
That I've always felt...

45:33.480 --> 45:36.080
..in getting to call you
my daughter.

45:53.160 --> 45:54.840
Bye, Dad.

46:14.880 --> 46:17.359
You took your time.

46:17.360 --> 46:19.000
Got there in the end.

46:20.200 --> 46:21.760
How can I help?

46:29.200 --> 46:31.079
You'll talk.

46:31.080 --> 46:33.599
And you'll talk a little more
on top, so we don't look

46:33.600 --> 46:35.999
into what he was doing here.

46:36.000 --> 46:38.160
Sorry, love, you've lost me.

46:39.640 --> 46:41.359
It's a nice place, this.

46:41.360 --> 46:45.399
Secure. With all the cameras.

46:45.400 --> 46:47.399
They picked up the two of you.

46:47.400 --> 46:49.160
You had a little chat.

46:51.640 --> 46:55.759
Common purpose.
That's the legal doctrine.

46:55.760 --> 46:59.319
Which means you'll both get
charged with attempted murder.

46:59.320 --> 47:01.320
Which fuels fear, does it not?

47:02.520 --> 47:05.480
You and Roy,
and your common purpose.

47:10.760 --> 47:12.999
I felt bad...

47:13.000 --> 47:15.160
..for what happened to your family.

47:16.640 --> 47:18.360
Not as bad as I did.

47:20.320 --> 47:23.560
And I always said to Roy
that it would be you.

47:26.000 --> 47:28.800
Hope you get the chance to
tell them that you were right.

47:31.080 --> 47:33.519
I'm allowed a phone call.

47:33.520 --> 47:34.880
It's too late.

47:40.160 --> 47:43.359
Can you get me my chair,
please, love?

47:43.360 --> 47:45.960
And my pills, from the bathroom?

47:50.320 --> 47:51.920
Dementia.

47:53.160 --> 47:55.759
Gets worse with the day.

47:55.760 --> 47:58.400
God knows what a judge
will make of it.

48:12.560 --> 48:14.959
Have you stopped the other thing?

48:14.960 --> 48:16.480
What other thing?

48:47.440 --> 48:48.960
ENGINE TURNS OVER

49:06.120 --> 49:08.520
PHONE RINGS

49:11.160 --> 49:13.160
PHONE RINGS

49:53.960 --> 49:56.039
I'm Roy Lynch.

49:56.040 --> 49:57.520
I know.

50:02.040 --> 50:03.799
The soldier.

50:03.800 --> 50:05.640
He was my brother.

50:06.880 --> 50:08.880
And there's something
about brothers.

50:11.720 --> 50:15.480
I used to say,
"Blood's thicker than water".

50:17.520 --> 50:20.880
But Maxie told me that's not
the original saying.

50:22.080 --> 50:25.640
It was actually about blood
being spilt on the field.

50:27.080 --> 50:29.840
And how that's the thickest
blood in the game.

50:32.440 --> 50:34.280
And that's OK.

50:35.600 --> 50:38.079
That makes sense, too.

50:38.080 --> 50:41.759
I don't know what Max told you,
but she had nothing to do with it.

50:41.760 --> 50:43.400
It was her house.

50:45.680 --> 50:47.919
Her husband was a degenerate

50:47.920 --> 50:49.440
and died in an act of patience.

50:50.560 --> 50:52.120
Your brother was...

50:53.840 --> 50:55.400
..unfortunate.

50:56.720 --> 51:00.919
And now, you have to do what you
have to do. I understand that.

51:00.920 --> 51:03.679
I respect that.

51:03.680 --> 51:05.640
But she has nothing to do with it.

51:09.800 --> 51:11.600
Maxie said that, too.

51:13.760 --> 51:15.320
That's fair.

51:50.880 --> 51:52.680
Are you from Leith, son?

51:54.960 --> 51:56.480
Aye.

51:58.160 --> 51:59.840
Well, that's something.

52:03.320 --> 52:04.960
DOOR SHUTS

52:40.400 --> 52:43.119
PHONE RINGS

52:43.120 --> 52:45.119
Hi.

52:45.120 --> 52:46.919
I'm here, and you're not.

52:46.920 --> 52:49.240
You don't need me. Not for this.

52:51.080 --> 52:53.119
The escape you wanted, it's not me.

52:53.120 --> 52:54.920
It's not the money, either.

52:56.760 --> 52:59.640
I can give you
the escape you wanted.

53:01.600 --> 53:04.359
I can release you.

53:04.360 --> 53:06.559
If that's what you want.

53:06.560 --> 53:08.119
What is this?

53:08.120 --> 53:09.719
I could've told you last night,

53:09.720 --> 53:12.080
but I'd only have done it
to hurt Roy.

53:13.680 --> 53:15.720
But now, it would be for you.

53:22.120 --> 53:24.279
What's in there?

53:24.280 --> 53:25.960
Everything you need.

53:27.960 --> 53:29.880
Everything you weren't given.

53:31.920 --> 53:33.960
You just need to ask.

53:36.320 --> 53:37.879
Tell me.

53:37.880 --> 53:40.160
And I want you to know,
this isn't...

53:42.920 --> 53:46.079
It's not about revenge, because
revenge only gets you halfway.

53:46.080 --> 53:48.480
What I've given you comes...

53:50.960 --> 53:53.799
..from love.

53:53.800 --> 53:55.480
And hope.

53:56.600 --> 53:58.320
For you and for me.

54:00.520 --> 54:02.440
I'm giving you what I never had.

54:05.080 --> 54:06.480
So you can heal.

54:08.720 --> 54:10.480
Like I never did.

54:14.560 --> 54:15.920
Tell me.

54:30.960 --> 54:33.600
DOOR CREAKS OPEN

54:37.480 --> 54:38.840
DOOR SHUTS

